 src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都好掛住我老竇<br />\n係佢地係有時係好煩 <br />\n但只不過係緊張我姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22463dfcec052bee237b9ab827155b7eaee36569","tid":2190191,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"哂撚氣啦"},{"pid":"e0bdeaa7eb30a5265fb99bbe7341bdcd15831136","tid":2190191,"uid":142509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"紅巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b961dd28fe23e19a4017a02e9f6aefdf4d93dcc","tid":2190191,"uid":48577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"頂住呀 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e765d34a58245a16487c47186b31167b3a2a3483","tid":2190191,"uid":21141,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"我老豆藍撚到發黑+典型廢老，由細打到我大，成日踐踏我自尊心，話我做乜都唔會掂<br />\n屋企人我只當有阿媽同家姐<br />\n老豆係我眼中只係住係同一個屋企既陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac1c2144dfbf8df2350864d8261256a31b1f62e","tid":2190191,"uid":359433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab87219487e261dcb071b8553ef948fad916414e","tid":2190191,"uid":38798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"一路以為你做廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9ccd0b1ed0ba4bd321fc5dd1ef43bb1bf677d7","tid":2190191,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcf77bf5bb815a4394a7178a69fdf9e356858a4","tid":2190191,"uid":268868,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:55:27.000Z","msg":"而家會咁諗咁就facetime下佢多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d29d10ee6cb11e2b91ceaea3ad1a1f16a68baf","tid":2190191,"uid":340796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"我以前去exchange嗰時好搞笑<br />\n叫屋企人唔好送我機，exchange 半年好平常仲有得Skype<br />\n其實我怕自己忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上咗機自己喊爆咗<br />\n到埗又喊，skype緊都眼紅紅咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰時就知一直都好依賴佢地，同佢地好close <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你識咁諗係好，佢地要嘅係見到你好，你要做嘅就係可以係有限嘅時間陪佢地多啲 有佢地心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adf4ea579be77b972fda1fb6e45481012274520","tid":2190191,"uid":310853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"其實都冇辦法 只好諗吓點樣做好啲"},{"pid":"e0ed669c520e81e1a514de7cfc4244516d6bdb82","tid":2190191,"uid":154892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感人"},{"pid":"ca6a727d717ee46d6bfd27ee8d01a13e9fad60c9","tid":2190191,"uid":267415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495d57ca17dc62c3f40b9c40029367b4f2cf5d61","tid":2190191,"uid":188310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T13:17:00.000Z","msg":"恨不得想我屋企人死 冚家剷 屌我老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face