,{"pid":"4737b1e6fb951d04e59b8bb8c0104eca912e0bea","tid":2190191,"uid":54311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c8d19e07a64b99a92c063e6cb4386a2f7078ed","tid":2190191,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"城仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好掛住我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efeb8325ebadd0101fa0e669a31f1cf025f74690","tid":2190191,"uid":75597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"之前睇啲去左外國既人講<br />\n假設父母已經60歲，當有80歲命<br />\n即係得返20年<br />\n每年見兩次<br />\n即係你只會見多父母40次...<br />\n個個講完都忍唔住"},{"pid":"daf36db470286547b608095c934e7008fe0046bc","tid":2190191,"uid":365674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"我明，我自己一個係澳洲讀左七年書諗住攞pr,最近屋企人講話想我番去陪佢哋....但係我重有幾個月就畢業，我想留住係到，試下搵工先。其實一個人係哩面真係會好掛住屋企，好掛住香港，好想番去....我自己一個係哩面越來越少朋友，因為好多人畢咗業之後都會返香港，冇咩事都冇乜照顧，有時覺得自己好可憐。屋企人其實又唔係話好支持我移民，好大壓力，好想放棄。樓主加油!"},{"pid":"8cd77ff5578052c0baf0719e46b67f376eb54427","tid":2190191,"uid":219736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:11:32.000Z","msg":"巴打出post 我 開咗通知㗎！<br />\nSupport u"},{"pid":"5af92274156af6b71b41f5bbf9bbbb16da76fc50","tid":2190191,"uid":324727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"睇到眼濕濕<br />\n至少你有好嘅屋企人<br />\n可能唔肯抽時間陪你 但盡力俾最好嘅嘢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1629c57d61c3878e82da0695cded4625de12ddf","tid":2190191,"uid":215201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ee61c338dfb01f5bbabb00f4a174c4a35e35